'''無緣社會'''（{{lang-ja|無縁社会}}）是2010年[[日本放送協會|日本放送協會]]《[[NHK特集|NHK特集]]》播出的探討[[人際關係|人際關係]]疏遠的專題，而後發展成一個[[新創詞|新創詞]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://anntw.com/articles/20141217-mt3L|title=日本無緣社會 漸漸影響台灣|author=陳清泉|work=[[台灣醒報|台灣醒報]]|date=2014-12-17|accessdate=2015-06-03|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921182237/https://anntw.com/articles/20141217-mt3L|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.japantoday.com/category/kuchikomi/view/no-of-people-dying-alone-rises-in-no-relationship-society|title = No. of people dying alone rises in 'no-relationship' society|accessdate = 2015-06-02|author = KUCHIKOMI|date = 2011-02-15|publisher = Japan Today|language = en|archive-date = 2016-04-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160422181459/http://www.japantoday.com/category/kuchikomi/view/no-of-people-dying-alone-rises-in-no-relationship-society|dead-url = no}}</ref>，意思為：「'''在高度成長的過程中，許多維繫人際關係的傳統逐漸被打破，個人與個人之間不再有任何關係及血緣'''」。

所謂「無緣」，是指一個人失去所有緣份連繫，總括三大緣：「社緣、血緣、地緣」<ref>{{Cite news|url = https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/daily/article/20141210/18963398|title = 無緣死|author = 曾志豪|date = 2014-12-10|work = [[香港蘋果日報|香港蘋果日報]]|accessdate = 2020-03-20|archive-date = 2020-03-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200320124804/https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/daily/article/20141210/18963398|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

